racter shall join the group",		/* [3] Buy iron rations, Normal */			"For 5 golden Eagles a weeks worth of light food rations sha"			"ll be yours",		/* [4] Buy a week rations, Normal */			"For 1 golden Eagle a week worth of food shall be yours",		/* [5] Buy a light drink, Normal */			"Care for a glass of beer?",		/* [6] Buy a strong drink, Normal */			"Some old liquorous wine?",		/* [7] Talk to the barman, Normal */			"Barmen can be a precious information source. Even invaluabl"			"e, if you are a good client…",		/* [8] Ask a ranger to join…, Normal */			"A new character shall join the group",		/* [9] Spend the night, Normal */			"I don't care what Apple's Human Interface says, I won't tel"			"l you what happens in this case, OK?",		/* [10] Buy rations, Normal */			"For 1 golden Eagle a week worth of food shall be yours",		/* [11] Ask a ruffian to join…, Normal */			"A new character shall join the group",		/* [12] Cast…, Normal */			"Displays the available spells window",		/* [13] Cast…, Grayed */			"The selected character isn't a spell-caster. Select a dream"			"er, or use a magic item, if you wish to cast a spell",		/* [14] Dismiss…, Normal */			"Selecting this option will send away the selected group mem"			"ber, forever!",		/* [15] Open game..., Normal */			"Lets you load a saved game, and start playing it",		/* [16] Save, Normal */			"Saves the current game on disk",		/* [17] Save As..., Normal */			"Saves the current game in a new file on disk",		/* [18] Page setup..., Normal */			"Configures the print settings",		/* [19] Print..., Normal */			"Prints the contents of the frontmost window",		/* [20] Quit, Normal */			"Leaves the Dream game system",		/* [21] Pause game, Normal */			"Stops the game clock",		/* [22] Sound, Normal */			"Sounds are muted. Selecting this item will enable them",		/* [23] Sound, Checked */			"Sounds are played. Selecting this item will mute them",		/* [24] Speech, Normal */			"Speech is muted. Selecting this item will make Dream read a"			"loud the description of the places you visit",		/* [25] Speech, Grayed */			"Speech is unavailable. You need PlainTalk software from App"			"le to enable it",		/* [26] Speech, Checked */			"Speech is enabled. Selecting this item will mute it",		/* [27] Transcript, Normal */			"The transcript windoid is hidden. Selecting this item will "			"show it. The trascript is a list of actions undertaken by ch"			"aracters and notices from the game system.",		/* [28] Transcript, Checked */			"The transcript windoid is active. Selecting this item will "			"hide it. The trascript is a list of actions undertaken by ch"			"aracters and notices from the game system.",		/* [29] Notification, Normal */			"Notification is off, so the game system won't display an al"			"ert when something potentially dangerous happens; such notes"			" will be sent to the trascript windoid",		/* [30] Notification, Checked */			"Notification is on, so the game system will display an aler"			"t when something potentially dangerous (like the lights turn"			"ing off) happens",		/* [31] Music, Normal */			"Music is muted. Selecting this item will allow Dream to pla"			"y its soundtrack while you play.",		/* [32] Music, Grayed */			"Music is unavailable. As soon as I find the time to write t"			"he music code I'll let you know, OK?",		/* [33] Music, Checked */			"The Dream soundtrack is playing. Selecting this item will m"			"ute it.",		/* [34] Search, Normal */			"The group will search the location they are in, digging, pa"			"tting walls and looking for tracks. But it's lengthy!",		/* [35] Rest, Normal */			"The group will set up camp and get eigth hours of beauty sl"			"eep",		/* [36] Battle order…, Normal */			"A window will appear and you'll be able to set up battle or"			"der",		/* [37] Battle order…, Grayed */			"You can't change battle order while a battle is taking plac"			"e",		/* [38] Battle order…, Checked */			"Click in the battle order window to change the disposition "			"of characters, then re-select this item when you're satisfie"			"d",		/* [39] Wait, Normal */			"The group will wait until midnight. This is useful if you w"			"ant to rest but the group isn't tired yet.",		/* [40] By Strength, Normal */			"Sorts the group by strength (the strongest character will be pos"			"itioned uppermost).",		/* [41] By Intelligence, Normal */			"Sorts the group by intelligence (the smartest character will be"			" positioned uppermost).",		/* [42] By Wisdom, Normal */			"Sorts the group by wisdom (the wisest character will be posit"			"ioned uppermost).",		/* [43] By Dexterity, Normal */			"Sorts the group by dexterity (the quickest character will be po"			"sitioned uppermost).",		/* [44] By Stamina, Normal */			"Sorts the group by stamina (the stoutest character will be posi"			"tioned uppermost).",		/* [45] By Charisma, Normal */			"Sorts the group by charisma (the handsomest character will be pos"			"itioned uppermost).",		/* [46] By Hit Points, Normal */			"Sorts the group by hit points. This is relative to the curr"			"ent situation, not the maximum HP.",		/* [47] Buy amber, Normal */			"Amber is indispensable to cast some spells",		/* [48] Buy bat guano, Normal */			"Bat guano is smelly but indispensable to cast some spells",		/* [49] Buy cure potion, Normal */			"A cure potion is indispensable to cast some spells",		/* [50] Buy glass lens, Normal */			"A small glass lens is indispensable to cast some spells",		/* [51] Shoot, normal */			"If your character owns a throwing weapon, pressing ‘T’ you'll"			"be allowed to aim at enemy monsters"	}};resource 'STR#' (1001, "Balloon Help String 2") {	{		/* [1] Buy magnet, Normal */			"A magnet is indispensable to cast some spells",		/* [2] Buy mushroom, Normal */			"Some mushrooms are indispensable to cast some spells",		/* [3] Buy quicksilver, Normal */			"Quicksilver is indispensable to cast some spells",		/* [4] Buy silver mirror, Normal */			"A silver mirror is indispensable to cast some spells",		/* [5] Ask a mage to join…, Normal */			"A new wizard shall join the group",		/* [6] About Akko's Dream, Normal */			"Shows info about the Dream application",		/* [7] About this scenario, Normal */			"Shows information about the current game scenario",		/* [8] Pray and repent, Normal */			"What do you expect? You stay here and pray, that's it.",		/* [9] Make an offer, Normal */			"A hundred golden Eagles for the poors would be appreciated",		/* [10] Ask a paladin to join…, Normal */			"A new paladin shall join the group. If he likes you.",		/* [11] Cure graze, Normal */			"The selected character will be cured 1-8 hit points of dama"			"ge by the High Priest",		/* [12] Cure wound, Normal */			"The selected character will be cured 3-18 hit points of dam"			"age by the High Priest",		/* [13] Cure gash, Normal */			"The selected character will be cured 10-100 hit points of d"			"amage by the High Priest",		/* [14] Cure all wounds, Normal */			"Everybody will be fully cured by the High Priest",		/* [15] Cure illness, Normal */			"The selected character will be cured by the High Priest",		/* [16] Cure poison, Normal */			"The selected character's blood will be purified by the High"			" Priest",		/* [17] Restore level, Normal */			"The selected character's lost experience levels will be res"			"tored by the High Priest",		/* [18] Raise dead, Normal */			"The High Priest will resurrect the selected character",		/* [19] Buy holy water, Normal */			"For 50 golden Eagles a vial of Holy Water shall be yours",		/* [20] Ask a cleric to join…, Normal */			"A new character shall join the group",		/* [21] OK, Normal */			"Click this button when you are satisfied with your choice",		/* [22] OK, Grayed */			"Drag the spells from the right to the book at the left, and"			" then you'll be able to click OK",		/* [23] Cancel, Normal */			"If you cancel, the scroll will be left untouched",		/* [24] Cancel, Grayed */			"It makes no sense to cancel now! If you did, you wouldn't g"			"ain new spells!",		/* [25] Restart, Normal */			"Clicking this button, you'll Undo your choices",		/* [26] OK, Normal */			"Click this button when you are satisfied with the spells yo"			"u have memorized",		/* [27] Join, Normal */			"Clicking this button the new character will join the group",		/* [28] Join, Grayed */			"Type a name for the new character, then click Join",		/* [29] Cancel, Normal */			"Clicking this button you'll leave the new member alone, and"			" the group shall stay as before",		/* [30] Reroll, Normal */			"Clicking this button, the character's statistics shall be r"			"ecalculated at random"	}};